<plot>In 19th-century Tacubaya, the daughter (Mapy Cortés) of a French pastry maker is to marry the mayor of the town (Domingo Soler), but her heart is said to be inclined more to an officer (Pedro Armendáriz). The sentimental conflict causes the famous historical episode known as "pastry war".</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?310104</url></doc>
